text: Mike Nash (born 1965 in Limerick, Ireland) is a retired Irish sportsperson. He played hurling with his local club South Liberties and was a member of the Limerick senior inter-county team in the 1990s. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:South Liberties hurlers Category:Limerick inter-county hurlers Category:Munster inter-provincial hurlers
